---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="relative min-h-[70vh] text-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/90 via-black/70 to-black/90 md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-black/80 md:via-black/50 md:to-transparent z-10 rounded-b-lg"
    >
    </div>
    <video
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-b-lg"
      aria-label="Video de fondo mostrando interfaces de software financiero"
    >
      <source src="/herobg.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      <track
        kind="captions"
        src="/captions/hero-video.vtt"
        srclang="es"
        label="Español"
      />
    </video>
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative h-full max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 z-20 py-12 md:py-20"
  >
    <div class="h-full flex flex-col min-h-[calc(70vh-4rem)]">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-sky-500/30 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm mb-6 self-start"
      >
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span
            class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-sky-400 opacity-75"
          ></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-sky-500"
          ></span>
        </span>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
            <span class="font-bold text-white">CMMI</span>
            <span class="text-white">DEV</span>
            <span class="text-sky-400">/3</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-sky-400 align-top">℠</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400"
            >Exp. 2027-12-22 / Appraisal #25953</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center max-w-3xl">
        <h1
          class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight"
        >
          Impulsamos la <span class="gradient-text relative inline-block"
            >tecnología
            <svg
              class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full"
              viewBox="0 0 358 8"
              fill="none"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                d="M1 5.26C90.3333 2.42667 267.667 -0.406667 357 5.26"
                stroke="#00BAE9"
                stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
          <br class="md:hidden" /><span class="md:ml-3">de tu negocio</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-2xl">
          Más de 25 años ofreciendo tecnología y asesoría en sistemas de
          información para empresas como la tuya.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a
            href="mailto:ventas@tecnoevolucion.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-[#012537] rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          >
            <Icon name="tabler:mail" class="w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true" />
            Contáctanos
          </a>
          <a
            href="#productos"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 border border-white/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
          >
            <span>Ver soluciones</span>
            <Icon
              name="tabler:arrow-right"
              class="w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out"
            />
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-white/10 pt-8 mt-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">+25</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Años de experiencia</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">+15</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Clientes activos</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #067ebb, #00bae9);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
</style>
